Small php framework used to convert CSV file to any other formats.

Conversions are implemented using the strategy pattern.

The following strategies are available :
 * CSV -> HTML
 * CSV -> PDF (using http://www.digitaljunkies.ca/dompdf/)

The following templates are available :
 * Scrum cards

 CLI usage examples :

  # Displays global help, lists available commands
  php ./bin/convert.php -h

  # Displays help for a specific command
  php ./bin/convert.php <command> -h

  #Â Converts a CSV file to PDF
  php ./bin/convert.php \
     --output-file=cards.pdf \
     --map=name,phone,email \
     to-dompdf \
     --templates_dir=./templates/businesscards \
      /home/jdoe/contacts.csv
